"COMPOUND() umsebenzi ubuyisela ixabiso lozaliso, inikwa inqununu, umyinge "
"oqhelekileyo wenzala, udityaniso oluqukuqelayo kunye nexesha. Umzekelo: "
"$5000 kwi 12% inzala idityaniswa ngesiqingatha nge 5 minyaka izakubaye "
"COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) okanye $9030.56."

