"uyizalise nge 8%, iyonke emvakweminyaka eyi 20 izakuba yi "
"FV_annuity(500;0.08;20) okanye $22,880.98. Lo msebenzi wenza iintlawulo "
"ezenziweyo kwisiphelo sethuba ngalinye."

