msgid "<title>PV</title>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4045
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PV() function returns the present value of an investment -- the value "
"today of a sum of money in the future, given the rate of interest or "
"inflation. For example if you need $1166.40 for your new computer and you "
"want to buy it in two years while earning 8% interest, you need to start "
"with PV(1166.4;0.08;2) or $1000."
msgstr ""
"PV() umsebenzi ubuyisela ixabiso elikhoyo lokuzalisa -- ixabiso namhlanje "
"lodibaniso lwemali kwixesha elizayo, unikwe umyinge wenzala okanye isiwo "
"sexabiso lemali. Umzekelo ukuba ufuna i $1166.40 ye computer yakho entsha "
"kwaye ufuna ukuyithenga kwiminyaka emibini ngexesha usamkela i 8% inzala, "
"ufuna ukuqala nge PV(1166.4;0.08;2) okanye $1000."

