#, no-c-format
msgid "PV(1166.4;0.08;2) equals 1000"
msgstr "PV(1166.4;0.08;2) ilingana 1000"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4065
#, no-c-format
msgid "PV_ANNUITY"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4066
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PV_ANNUITY() function returns the present value of an annuity or stream "
"of payments. For example: a \"million dollar\" lottery ticket that pays "
"$50,000 a year for 20 years, with an interest rate of 5%, is actually worth "
"PV_ANNUITY(50000;0.05;20) or $623,111. This function assumes that payments "
"are made at the end of each period."
msgstr ""
"PV_annuity() umsebenzi ubuyisela ixabiso elikhoyo lonyaka okanye uqukuqelo "
"lwentlawulo. Umzekelo: i \"sigidi se dollar\" itikiti leloto elihlawula i "
"$50,000 ngonyaka kwi 20 yeminyaka, ngomyinge wenzala we 5%, iyasebenza ngqo "
"PV_annuity(50000;0.05;20) okanye $623,111. Lo msebenzi wenza iintlawulo ezo "
"ezenziwa kwisiphelo sexesha ngalinye."

#. Tag: para
