#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:7698
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHIDIST"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7699
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The CHIDIST() function returns the probability value from the indicated Chi "
"square that a hypothesis is confirmed."
msgstr "MINUTES() umsebenzi ubuyisela ixabiso lemizuzu kuchazo lwexesha."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7700
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"CHIDIST compares the Chi square value to be given for a random sample that "
"is calculated from the sum of (observed value-expected value)^2/expected "
"value for all values with the theoretical Chi square distribution and "
"determines from this the probability of error for the hypothesis to be "
"tested."
msgstr ""
"          Ibuyisela ixabiso olwenzekayo kwisikweri se Chi eyalathiweyo "
"yokuba hypothesis iqinisekisiwe. CHIDIST ithelekisa ixabiso lesikweri seChi "
"sinikelwe isampuli ejikelezayo ebalwa kwisixa se (elibukelweyo ixabiso-"
"ixabiso elilindelweyo)^2/ixabiso elilindelweyo yawo onke amaxabiso "
"ngokubhala unikezelo lwesikweri seChi kwaye igqiba koku kwenziwa kwemposiso "
"ye hypothesis ivavanywe.        "

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7705
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHIDIST(number;degrees_freedom)"
msgstr "CHIDIST(inani, amaqondo_inkululeko)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:7710
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom"
msgstr "amaqondo enkululeko"

