msgstr "CHIDIST(13.27;5) ibuyisela 0.021"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:7719
#, no-c-format
msgid "COMBIN"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The COMBIN() function calculates the count of possible combinations. The "
"first parameter is the total count of elements. The second parameter is the "
"count of elements to choose. Both parameters should be positive and the "
"first parameter should not be less than the second. Otherwise the function "
"returns an error."
msgstr ""
"COMBIN() umsebenzi ubala ubalo lwendibaniso ezenzekayo. Eyokuqala i "
"parameter lubalo olupheleleyo lweziqalelo. Eyesibini i parameter lubalo "
"lweziqalelo zokukhethwa. Zombini i parameters zinokubazezi vumelanayo kwaye "
"eyokuqala i parameter ayinakuba ngaphantsi kuneyesibini. Kungenjalo "
"umsebenzi ubuyisela imposiso."

