"DOLLAR() umsebenzi uguqula inani kokubhaliweyo usebenzise imali yeloo lizwe "
"ifomati, ngenani leshumi elingqukuviweyo kwindawo ethile. Nangaona igama iyi "
"DOLLAR, lomsebenzi uzakwenza uguqulelo njenge locale yangoku."

