#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:9563
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The FIND() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text."
msgstr ""
"FIND() umsebenzi ufumana umtya wokubhaliweyo omnye (fumana_okubhaliweyo) "
"ngaphakathi kokunye okubhaliweyo (ngaphakathi_kokubhaliweyo) kwaye ibuyisela "
"inana loqalo lwencopho fumana_okubhaliweyo ukusuka kwi leta esekhohlo "
"yomsebenzi wangaphakathi_kokubhaliweyo."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter start_num specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 1. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 1."
msgstr ""
"i Parameter qala_num ikhankanya umsebenzi apho uphendlo luzakuqalwa. "
"Umsebenzi wokuqala ngumsebenzi onenani 1. Ukuba qala_num ishiyiwe, iqashelwe "
"ukuba iyi 1."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use function SEARCH, but unlike SEARCH, FIND is case-sensitive "
"and does not allow wildcard characters."
msgstr ""
"Uyakwazi ukusebenzisa umsebenzi SEARCH, kodwa ngokungafani SEARCH, FIND "
"ngumzekelo onovakalelo kwaye akavumeli abasebenzisi be wildcard."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9571
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND(find_text;within_text;start_num)"
msgstr "FIND(fumana_okubhaliweyo;ngaphakathi_okubhaliweyo;qala_num)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9575 functions.docbook:9612 functions.docbook:10112
#: functions.docbook:10145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text you want to find"
msgstr "Okubhaliweyo ofuna ukufumana"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9576 functions.docbook:9613 functions.docbook:10113
#: functions.docbook:10146
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text which may contain find_text"
msgstr "Okubhaliweyo okunokuqulatha fumana_okubhaliweyo"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies index to start the search"
msgstr "Ikhankanya isalthisi sokuqala uphendlo"

